Package org.apache.activemq

Interface BlobMessage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Message, Message
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActiveMQBlobMessage
    public interface BlobMessage
extends Message
    Represents a message which has a typically out of band Binary Large Object (BLOB)
